header: ['BRIEF-FCA And PSA Focused on Their Recovery To Reach Merger Closing Date in Best Possible Financial Situation - Statement']
article content: ['July 3 (Reuters) - ', '* FCA AND PSA TEAMS ARE WORKING EFFICIENTLY AND IN A HIGHLY COLLABORATIVE MODE TOWARDS THE CLOSING OF THE MERGER - STATEMENT PROVIDED BY PSA GROUP SPOKESMAN ', '* PSA AND FCA ARE FOCUSED ON THEIR RECOVERY IN ORDER TO REACH THE CLOSING DATE IN THE BEST POSSIBLE FINANCIAL SITUATION - STATEMENT PROVIDED BY PSA GROUP SPOKESMAN (Reporting by Gilles Guillaume Editing by Mathieu Rosemain)']
